verbose_text: Western blot results showed minimal nuclear NFATc1 protein expression in untreated osteoclasts, while Mt sonicate treatment significantly enhanced the expression of NFATc1 protein in osteoclast nuclei, indicating that Mt Sonicate significantly enhanced differentiation of osteoclasts (XREF_FIG).
evidence: NFATc1 protein in osteoclast nuclei, indicating that Mt Sonicate significantly enhanced differentiation
